command.text: Nilreetron drank this as he battled the goblins under the city.
This is a pub not a fountain.
A friend once ordered that drink it began an adventure.
Have you heard of Terinalyp? Trapped out of time they say.
You pointed ears like your tea.
Not a typical drink for a non elf.
Alas we are all out at the moment.
Did you hear of the grave under the city?
Come back with a story to tell.
Thank you for returning the stone golem.
Someone has taken control of the earthen guardian. Find it for a reward.
